OL,5, The owner of Facebook and Instagram was
OL,6, hit by a fall in advertising sales in  
OL,7, the three months to July which caused  
OL,8, the first year-on-year revenue decline 
OL,9, in the firm's history.                 
OL,11,FMeta's total revenue slipped 1% to     
OL,12,F$28.8bn (#23.7bn), but the company     
OL,13,Ffended off a decline in users.         
OL,15,FAnalysts fear the company's growth may 
OL,16,Fhave peaked after years of large gains.
OL,18,FRivals such as TikTok have eroded its  
OL,19,Fpopularity, while more firms are       
OL,20,Fcompeting for ad spending.             
